\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
{\cal B}_{x}^{h}={\cal A}_{f(x)}^{g}{\cal B}_{x}^{f}.
\]

\end_inset

If, in addition, 
\begin_inset Formula ${\cal B}_{x}^{f}$
\end_inset

 is an F-derivative then 
\begin_inset Formula ${\cal B}_{x}^{h}$
\end_inset

 is an F-derivative as well.
\end_layout

